milestones.description: Paras Khadka and Sompal Kami's 28-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 13 between Paras Khadka and Khakurel
Sompal Kami and Aarif Sheikh's 24-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 16 between Paras Khadka and Rohit Paudel
Sompal Kami has become the top scorer for NEP in ODIs with 118 runs, going past Airee's 92
Bhandari has broken the record for most dismissals (3) in ODIs for NEP, going past Anil Sah's 2
This is the lowest match aggregate (229) involving teams U.A.E. & Nepal in ODIs
Bhandari has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (3) in ODIs for NEP, going past Anil Sah's 2
Aarif Sheikh has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for NEP, going past Airee
